race.comment: COSMIC CHARGER (1) settled well back from a wide draw last time then wound up strongly to finish fourth over 1200m at Swan Hill. Drew wide there and now gets the switch inside. Profiles nicely for this for the top yard. NEWS TRAVELS FAST (2) resumes. He's mixed his form but has trialled well leading into this. No surprise if he was able to get off the mark. SINCERE SMILE (9) is a maiden galloper who hasn't raced since finishing 6 lengths back in fifth over 1200m at Mornington six months ago. Fitter for three lead-up trials, including a win. Finds a far more suitable race now, rates well. BEACH COUTURE (10) debuts. Trials have possessed merit.
